Ingredients 

Serves: 16 
Brownies
125g butter
1 cup (220g) caster sugar
2 eggs
1 teaspoon vanilla essence
4 tablespoons cocoa powder
1/2 cup (60g) plain flour
1/4 teaspoon salt
1/4 teaspoon baking powder

Icing

60g butter, softened
2 tablespoons cocoa
1 tablespoon honey
1 teaspoon vanilla essence
125g (3/4 cup) icing sugar
